5|$|The <b>Patrol</b> <b>Leaders</b> Training Unit (or PLTU) is a 7- to 12-day course run {{at various}} venues around South Africa. PLTU {{is a very}} {{physically}} and mentally strenuous course, open to Scouts who are over 14½ years old and have achieved their Adventurer advancement badge.|$|R
